registerUserByObject

public java.lang.Long registerUserByObject(java.lang.Object regObjectObj)
Add a user register by an Object see [registerUser] for the index of the Object To allow the registering the config_key *allow_frontend_register* has to be the value 1 otherwise the user will get an error code

参数：
regObjectObj -
返回：
new users_id OR null if an exception, -1 if an error, -4 if mail already taken, -5 if username already taken, -3 if login or pass or mail is empty
